1
00:00:02,002 --> 00:00:03,604
I became a YouTuber to make

2
00:00:05,039 --> 00:00:06,474
everyone laugh and smile

3
00:00:07,274 --> 00:00:10,478
like I made my grandma laugh.

4
00:00:11,879 --> 00:00:15,349
Every day I look for material
to spark everyone's interests.

5
00:00:15,750 --> 00:00:17,852
I act, film…

6
00:00:18,686 --> 00:00:20,921
and edit at night without sleep.

7
00:00:21,188 --> 00:00:24,792
But no matter how much money I earn,
I have no time to spend that money.

8
00:00:27,194 --> 00:00:29,230
When I go out, people look down on me.

9
00:00:29,897 --> 00:00:31,866
They tell me that I make easy money.

10
00:00:32,533 --> 00:00:36,771
They talk trash about me
and pick on me. I've had enough of that!

11
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:43,444
What am I doing?

12
00:00:45,579 --> 00:00:49,717
I really didn't want to do
a soy sauce drinking prank!

13
00:00:50,351 --> 00:00:54,855
Nishikigoi-carp bath is not good
for the poor Nishikigoi carp.

14
00:00:54,922 --> 00:00:58,159
But now, unless I bungee jump

15
00:00:58,225 --> 00:01:02,263
off the Tokyo Tower,
no one will accept me.

16
00:01:08,169 --> 00:01:10,871
I'm done.

17
00:01:12,773 --> 00:01:17,378
I'm done with this lifestyle…

18
00:01:34,495 --> 00:01:37,097
I think it's fine to run away.

19
00:01:52,046 --> 00:01:54,081
It must have been hard for you.

20
00:01:55,716 --> 00:02:00,154
I'm buying this house,
no matter how much it costs.

21
00:02:07,495 --> 00:02:09,430
Thank you very much.

22
00:02:19,540 --> 00:02:22,510
This is the application form.

23
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:27,481
Chief Sangenya, let's go now.

24
00:02:30,217 --> 00:02:31,418
