131
00:10:09,409 --> 00:10:10,744
Chief Sangenya,

132
00:10:10,811 --> 00:10:14,781
let's stop staying here for now,
and go home.

133
00:10:15,082 --> 00:10:17,017
After I sell this place today,
I'll go home.

134
00:10:17,451 --> 00:10:18,719
