139
00:10:27,127 --> 00:10:30,297
-Mr. Nikumaru?
-Fans need to stay outside.

140
00:10:30,864 --> 00:10:32,733
Oh? He's…

141
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:35,302
Yes, he's Mr. Nikumaru, the YouTuber.

142
00:10:36,503 --> 00:10:38,705
I've been waiting for you, Mr. Nikumaru.

143
00:10:40,741 --> 00:10:42,576
You finally realized it, didn't you?

144
00:10:43,744 --> 00:10:48,949
I can imagine how hard it must have been
at the peaceful mountainside.

145
00:10:50,350 --> 00:10:53,487
You don't need a peaceful life.

146
00:10:54,021 --> 00:10:56,456
What you need is people watching you,

147
00:10:57,057 --> 00:10:59,359
praises and storms of criticisms.

148
00:11:00,093 --> 00:11:03,263
Those are the things
that give you the will to live.

149
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:06,566
How do you know that?

150
00:11:08,001 --> 00:11:12,072
The war photographer goes to war
despite the danger.

151
00:11:12,139 --> 00:11:16,109
It's because they need to be
in danger to feel alive.

152
00:11:16,676 --> 00:11:19,646
Mountain climbers climb
to the summit of Mt. Everest

153
00:11:19,713 --> 00:11:22,015
despite the danger of getting lost,
because their life

154
00:11:22,082 --> 00:11:26,253
is not fulfilling unless they are in
a life-or-death situation.

155
00:11:27,354 --> 00:11:29,589
Mr. Nikumaru, you are the same.

156
00:11:30,357 --> 00:11:32,559
As a YouTuber,
you struggle to find material,

157
00:11:32,626 --> 00:11:36,029
lose sleep, get abused by trolls,

158
00:11:36,096 --> 00:11:39,433
and get criticized.
Otherwise you don't feel alive.

159
00:11:42,803 --> 00:11:44,271
You are right.

160
00:11:45,172 --> 00:11:47,541
Then why are you running away?

161
00:11:48,942 --> 00:11:51,878
Put your life on the line
and continue to be a YouTuber!

162
00:11:52,846 --> 00:11:55,015
Expose yourself
in this fully exposed house,

163
00:11:55,482 --> 00:11:58,785
and upload videos
that only you can create!

164
00:11:59,953 --> 00:12:03,890
Just like your grandmother
who saw your talent as she raised you.

165
00:12:03,957 --> 00:12:07,294
You will be the center of attention.
You'll be trolled.

166
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:08,795
Come under fire.

167
00:12:08,862 --> 00:12:10,730
And be the YouTuber
who lays his life on the line.

168
00:12:11,064 --> 00:12:13,233
You will shine in that moment of crisis!

169
00:12:14,034 --> 00:12:16,603
There is no need to fear
being under fire on the net!

170
00:12:20,207 --> 00:12:21,341
Right.

171
00:12:22,776 --> 00:12:23,910
That is right.

172
00:12:26,246 --> 00:12:28,748
Why didn't I buy this house?

173
00:12:29,549 --> 00:12:33,220
It is not too late.

174
00:12:33,987 --> 00:12:35,155
Really?

175
00:12:35,622 --> 00:12:40,293
Mr. Nikumaru, will you buy
this house for ¥100 million?

176
00:12:41,595 --> 00:12:46,099
Wait one second.
You are ripping him off too much.

177
00:12:46,166 --> 00:12:50,604
Yeah! ¥100 million! ¥100 million!

178
00:12:50,670 --> 00:12:53,240
¥100 million!

179
00:12:53,306 --> 00:12:54,741
¥100 million!

180
00:12:54,808 --> 00:12:58,478
¥100 million! ¥100 million!

181
00:12:58,545 --> 00:13:02,549
¥100 million! ¥100 million!

182
00:13:08,688 --> 00:13:12,959
I will buy it.

183
00:13:14,294 --> 00:13:17,998
I will pay ¥100 million in cash!

184
00:13:18,298 --> 00:13:19,366
Cash?

185
00:13:21,668 --> 00:13:23,270
-I've got him.
-Cash!

186
00:13:23,336 --> 00:13:26,806
Cash! Cash! Cash!

187
00:13:27,174 --> 00:13:29,242
-Cash!
-Mr. Nikumaru,

188
00:13:29,309 --> 00:13:32,179
