on this application form?

189
00:13:32,245 --> 00:13:33,246
Signature!

190
00:13:33,313 --> 00:13:34,714
Okay.

191
00:13:34,781 --> 00:13:38,818
Signature! Signature!

192
00:13:38,885 --> 00:13:42,656
Signature! Signature!

193
00:13:44,624 --> 00:13:46,927
The fully exposed house
